oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kay and Al Carvell - The Original Lone Star Cowboy and Girl
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Kay and Al Carvell: The Original Lone Star Cowboy and Girl. The recording features performances by Kay Carvell, Al Carvell, David Carvell, and Katherine Carvell. The recording is from an unidentified date. The tape was dubbed from a cassette recording on an unidentified date.
